Articles.Content:
The P50 Variants! This craft has a design so the propellers are in the back.

(from left to right) P-50P, P-50PM, and P-50E. The difference between them is that they have different engines. The P-50P has a propeller that is slightly less powerful than the P-50PM. But the P-50E has a turbojet.

Hope you like it! ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif)
